rows.label: tlk45320351_02_msg0001
rows.name:
With Wadatsumi no longer by His
Majesty's side, we of the Imperial
Guard must redouble our efforts...

rows.label: tlk45320351_02_msg0002
rows.name:
You are trusted associates of
the Emperor. You may pass.

rows.label: tlk45320351_02_msg0102
rows.name:
Fear not - we of the Carraig Imperial
Guard will keep the Emperor safe
no matter what may transpire!

rows.label: tlk45320351_02_msg0103
rows.name:
Please continue with your
journey in the knowledge that
His Majesty is well protected.
